    "**MARYAM** \n",
    "* view_all_recipes(recipes)\tPrints a numbered list of all recipes with key details\n",
    "* filter_by_category(recipes)\t Stretch — shows only recipes from a chosen category\n",
    "* generate_shopping_list(recipes)\t Stretch — combines ingredients from multiple recipes"
   ]
